✨ Features

👤 Personalized User Profiles

Users can create their own profile and choose a customizable boy or girl character. Progress, rewards, and study statistics are linked to each profile.

💓 Today's Pulse (Mood Tracking)

Students can record their daily mood, such as Calm, Motivated, Stressed, or Exhausted. This helps the system understand emotional patterns and provide a more personalized study experience.

🎯 Today's Aim

Allows users to set daily study goals and stay focused on what they want to achieve throughout the day.

✅ Smart Task Management

Students can add, edit, organize, and complete tasks while tracking their daily productivity.

🍅 Adaptive Pomodoro Timer

The Pomodoro timer automatically adjusts study and break durations based on the user's attention span, focus levels, and study performance.

📖 Review Habits Tracking

Tracks revision activities such as reading, flashcards, practice questions, and note revision. The system uses this data to improve study recommendations.

🤖 Adaptive Study Recommendations

The application analyzes attention span, mistakes, mood patterns, and revision habits to suggest personalized study plans and revision schedules.

🪙 Beans Reward System

Students earn Beans by completing tasks, maintaining study streaks, and using Pomodoro sessions. Beans can be spent on character customizations and rewards.

👥 Friends & Collaborative Learning

Users can add friends, study together, share progress, and stay motivated through healthy competition and collaboration.

📊 Analytics Dashboard

Provides insights into study time, focus levels, task completion rates, revision consistency, and overall learning progress.

🎨 Customizable Study Environments

Users can switch between different study backgrounds:

📚 Library

☕ Coffee Shop

🏮 Japanese Café
